            . I am a carpenter. I was in Chiswell-street, near Whitebread's brewhouse, and saw the prisoner take the handkerchief from the gentleman's pocket- I gave the alarm, and saw him stopped by an officer.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290409-88-person922">
