                     <interp inst="t18290409-88-person922" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . About half-past four o'clock I saw the prisoner running towards me, and stopped him; he dropped this handkerchief - I did not see it taken; the prisoner had 9 1/2d. in his pocket.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written defence, pleading poverty.</p>
